<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Me, Myself, and I</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
        }

        header {
            background-color: pink;
            color: black;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1rem;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .section {
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .h2 {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .profile-img {
            border-radius: 50%;
            width: 250px;
            height: 250px;
            object-fit: cover;
            text-align: center; /* Added */
            margin: 0 auto; /* Added */
        }

        .picture-text {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .picture-text img {
            width: 150px;
            margin-right: 20px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            /* Removed duplicated width and height */
        }

        .picture-text .text {
            flex: 1;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h2>Front-End Web Developer | Designer</h2>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="picture-text">
            <img src="profile.pic.jpg" alt="Profile Picture">
            <div class="profile-img">
                <h1>Hi! I'm Maggie. Let me tell you about me.</h1>
            </div>
        </div>

        <section class="section">
            <p>My name is Maggie. I'm a beginner front-end developer and designer. I went to the University of New Hampshire where I earned a Bachelor's degree in Zoology and an Associate's degree in Applied Animal Science focusing on Veterinary Technology. This is my first attempt at coding to see if it's something I can do. I've been teaching myself and working as a veterinary technician for the past 4 years.</p>
            <h3>Things I like to do</h3>
            <p>In my spare time, I enjoy reading, writing poetry, playing games with my friends, and coding. My goal by the end of the year is to create a project for my portfolio and transition into a career in tech. I also love spending time with my pomeranians.</p>
            <h4>Things I want to achieve</h4>
            <p>I want to create a weather app, a Netflix clone, and a website from front to back. I also aim to make the switch in careers.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="section">
            <h4>Portfolio</h4>
            <p>Me, Myself, and I</p>
        </section>

        <section class="section">
            <h4>Contact</h4>
            <p>
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/margaret-frye-53346623a/">LinkedIn</a><br>
                <a href="https://github.com/magicmags-portfolios">Github</a><br>
                <a href="mailto:contact@magsCoding@gmail.com">Email</a><br>
            </p>
        </section>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
